column5: It may be coincidences but he gave me what I wished for, but not the things that I really wanted the most... All I want is someone to come home to and love me...
I feel you I do the same... I even drive like a maniac just in the hope that I will end this way

I hope so :/

Better be harsh than me not getting what you say, its okay I get over it lol
Yeah sorry I know... Thanks for your help, I‘ll be a better person I promise
I think I did, I‘m just a very naive and blind person in relationships...
Normally I care about ppl and I think many of my friends would tell you the same but I just didnt have any sympathy for him... Yeah stupid from my side...

I‘m 18 she‘s 19

No I knew her bf probably wouldn‘t be happy but if I‘m honest I never gave a shit abt him, until now when I realized I could be in his position

Hmm... idk what to say you are probably right but I dint want to believe it if I‘m honest, a part of me thinks that the flirting might just be a joke that got out of hand and because I still have feeling for her I might have picked em up as signals... if thats not the case you are 100% right and I am just to stupid to realize it...

Well ok you‘re right on the first point but other than that she never was mean afaik

I mean she‘s shy in public, not while texting and I didnt creat a fake person in my mind, I know some of her friends and they all said she was shy, and she does appear so.

She isnt really mean to anyone, she‘s more shy and was never mean to me, except for kinda roleplaying while texting but thats a different thing... She was even very caring when I recently had an accident and asked me 100 times if I was doing better or saying I should visit the doc etc
Yeah... I am not the brightest light and I feel stupid for it... Trust me a few hours ago I would have taken a bullet for her
You‘re right, the thing is all my friends told me to fight for her no matter what it costs if I really live her... Man I could face slap myself now
Argh I hate my self for always loving the wrong girls...
I think it would fuck me up even more than when she told me she was taken...
Hmm okay... do you think forever or for now?
Yup! Luca Todesco just said that in his talk! So I *guess* if we see a big difference in a part of the low level stuff in iboot those things might have changed for the bootrom aswell.
Sure but either I‘m doing it wrong or it doesnt work
